title: The Worry Bucket
itunes:title: The Worry Bucket
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

If you're a worrier, then listen up! In this podcast I describe the best way for you to set aside worry and move toward finding a solution.

Worry is totally unproductive. Our moms did it. We think we are good people if we are worrying. We're not! All worry does is keep us doing nothing except trying to figure out the next disaster.
